WEBVTT

00:08.473 --> 00:10.869
You can't put Italy without football.

00:11.191 --> 00:14.557
ACTV came about to actually work with the human body...

00:14.687 --> 00:18.449
...and bring the best out of what is already an amazing machine.

00:20.039 --> 00:22.719
By fusing athletic taping and compression,...

00:22.946 --> 00:28.275
...what we create is a system that enables faster energy supply to the muscles...

00:28.407 --> 00:30.327
...through the stimulation of the skin.

00:31.844 --> 00:36.516
They build in things that they believe to be true Italian flavor and detail.

00:37.181 --> 00:38.299
This is what we give back.

00:38.539 --> 00:41.645
This technology doesn't exist in football at this moment in time.

00:41.895 --> 00:44.257
We are the first to bring it to this field of play,...

00:44.371 --> 00:47.564
...and we are harmonizing it with classic Italian design...

00:47.729 --> 00:49.841
...and future human performance.

